show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/C9WUGL
show.description: Divorced on my anniversary and publicly shamed by his mistress, they never suspected I was American royalty—the daughter of the richest man in the country who secretly bankrolled my ex-husband's success. The universe balanced the scales when I unexpectedly married a dashing billionaire hours later. Now I navigate dual identities with wealth and power at my fingertips.
